      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed propagating uncertainty in power-law coefficients and viscosity. Hematocrit variability was excluded from the input distributions without justification. The dominant input drivers have not been ranked because no sensitivity analysis was conducted alongside the UQ; the team notes that sensitivity analysis is planned for a future revision. Achieved level 2 against required level 4.",
